{"name":"Mathlib.Algebra.Star.CHSH","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Algebra.CharP.Invertible","Mathlib.Data.Real.Sqrt"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.lean#L198-L252","name":"tsirelson_inequality","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.html#tsirelson_inequality","doc":"In a noncommutative ordered `*`-algebra over ℝ,\nTsirelson's bound for a CHSH tuple (A₀, A₁, B₀, B₁) is\n`A₀ * B₀ + A₀ * B₁ + A₁ * B₀ - A₁ * B₁ ≤ 2^(3/2) • 1`.\n\nWe prove this by providing an explicit sum-of-squares decomposition\nof the difference.\n\n(We could work over `ℤ[2^(1/2), 2^(-1/2)]` if we really wanted to!)\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.lean#L180-L182","name":"TsirelsonInequality.sqrt_two_inv_mul_self","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.html#TsirelsonInequality.sqrt_two_inv_mul_self","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.lean#L173-L177","name":"TsirelsonInequality.tsirelson_inequality_aux","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.html#TsirelsonInequality.tsirelson_inequality_aux","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.lean#L127-L150","name":"CHSH_inequality_of_comm","kind":"theorem","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.html#CHSH_inequality_of_comm","doc":"Given a CHSH tuple (A₀, A₁, B₀, B₁) in a *commutative* ordered `*`-algebra over ℝ,\n`A₀ * B₀ + A₀ * B₁ + A₁ * B₀ - A₁ * B₁ ≤ 2`.\n\n(We could work over ℤ[⅟2] if we wanted to!)\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/44c828ca5b12983ef1d4eea5c54f95c2ef52cb36/Mathlib/Algebra/Star/CHSH.lean#L106-L118","name"